title: The Complete Mr Magoo D1 1960 - 1961 - ReVamp1
description:
None of the files I will be uploading are mine, the credits go to others. 
All the files can be found on bittorrent sites. 
All have been re-encoded and cleaned up.
I will seed until there are enough seeders and then will upload more.

To everyone who don't hit and run but keep on seeding - THANKS.

This 2 disc set is compiled from 4 dvd5s which (I'm guessing) must have been 4 dvd9s originally.The original version had Portuguese menus only which have been replaced by English menus.There is no difference between the menus except the English text. 

No compression to make dvd9.

D1 has 70 episodes 

Enjoy
